description:
Valley of the dolls #2

My second minted objkt. The previous one is the moodboard of this collection. Made this design after my trip to Vietnam.

Take a story of Paj Ndau, a traditional textile arts of Hmong People to express a individual experiences of happiness and loss across generation.

Style and silhouette are layered looks and modified basic. The color scheme are multiple hues from blue to fuschia.
